Posted notice to the general public regarding the deadline of filing for payment of taxes and the benefits they will earn on account of payment of their property tax; 

Inquired with the Provincial Treasurer regarding the deputation of Barangay Treasurers to collect taxe; 

Assigned Revenue Collectors to the barangays to monitor collections. Such was undertaken last April 2018 up to December of the same year.

